250
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:50,160
♫I wanna thank you for making me feel♫

251
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:53,800
♫Just how beautiful love can be♫

252
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:56,120
♫Every chamber of my heart♫

253
00:20:56,140 --> 00:20:58,740
♫Will be yours from now on♫
♫Every chamber of my heart♫

254
00:20:58,770 --> 00:21:04,490
♫You're a godsent present from above♫

255
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:10,400
